                                <condition>
                                    <p>There are many traces of wear and especially the bottom right
                                        corner is often darker than the rest of the leaves. </p>
                                    <p>Ff. <locus from="29r" to="31v">29-31</locus> are missing the
                                        bottom outer corner, which has been cut off. </p>
                                    <p>There is damage from moisture and liquid at the outer edge of
                                        many leaves. </p>
                                    <p>The parchment has a few small holes.</p>
                                </condition>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout columns="1" writtenLines="21">
                                    <p>The main text is written in a single column, and most often
                                        has 21 lines per page but wide margins, that often contain
                                        Latin glossary. </p>
                                    <p> The size of the main column is approximately <dimensions type="written">
                                            <height quantity="70" unit="mm">70</height>
                                            <width quantity="55" unit="mm">55</width>
                                        </dimensions>. </p>
                                </layout>
